data.description: Don't miss this rare opportunity!!  One level living on a large river lot! With LOW specials, great location surrounded by mature trees, a large garage with a shop, makes this one a must see! This home offers a 300+ sq ft 3 season sunroom, three bedrooms, two bathrooms, a tandem garage with 2 parking spaces, a fully fenced yard, a large patio, new flooring, a newer roof and more. Take a look today!
